{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Appraise Your Item",
  "settings": [],
  "blocks": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Appraise Your Item"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}

<section class="appraisal-form">
  <div class="appraisal-container">
    <h2 class="appraisal-title">Appraise your item</h2>
    
    <form class="appraisal-upload-form" enctype="multipart/form-data">
      <label for="appraisal-photos" class="upload-area">
        <span>Upload Photos (up to 5)</span>
        <input 
          type="file" 
          id="appraisal-photos" 
          name="photos[]" 
          accept="image/*" 
          multiple 
          max="5" 
          style="display:none"
        >
      </label>

      <ul class="upload-instructions">
        <li>Upload multiple images of one (1) jewelry piece from multiple angles.</li>
        <li>Take photos in good lighting.</li>
        <li>Include close-ups of markings and stamps.</li>
        <li>Avoid including extra doodads in the image (best to take pictures of the jewelry on a plain white table).</li>
        <li>Phasellus interdum sed tortor vel mollis. Vivamus sagittis venenatis dolor, non sagittis quam dapibus quis.</li>
        <li>Cras in lectus semper, convallis mi eget, dignissim tellus.</li>
        <li>In vel ultrices lacus. Fusce varius risus a placerat tristique.</li>
        <li>Proin sagittis, tortor id ultricies suscipit, ante nulla facilisis leo, sit amet finibus arcu metus nec velit.</li>
        <li>Morbi dapibus magna eget tempus efficitur.</li>
      </ul>

      <button type="button" class="analyze-btn" disabled>Analyze</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.appraisal-form {
  padding: 40px 0;
}
.appraisal-container {
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}
.appraisal-title {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.upload-area {
  display: block;
  border: 2px dashed #ccc;
  padding: 50px 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  cursor: pointer;
  color: #666;
}
.upload-area:hover {
  background-color: #fafafa;
}
.upload-instructions {
  text-align: left;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: #444;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}
.upload-instructions li {
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}
.analyze-btn {
  background-color: #ccc;
  color: #fff;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border: none;
  cursor: not-allowed;
  border-radius: 4px;
}
</style>
